  <data name="Quack_LongDescription" errorCode="006" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Returns a table listing the tables in the DuckDB database at &lt;code&gt;database&lt;/code&gt;. An optional record parameter, &lt;code&gt;options&lt;/code&gt;, may be specified to control the following options:
